<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"/>
    <title>Wargamers Pledge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/reset.css" media="all"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/pledge.css" media="all"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/forms.css" media="all"/>
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->  
</head>
<body>
    <section id="wrapper">
        <header><span class="curl"></span>
            <h1>Wargamers Pledge</h1>
        </header>
        <div id="content">
            
    <form action="/collection/add" method="post">
        <div class="field">
            <label for="purchase_date">Purchase Date</label>
            <input type="date" name="purchase_date" id="purchase_date" value="[% form_data.purchase_date | html %]" />
        </div>
        
        <p>We ask you to describe the packs of miniatures you buy so we can
        collect data on what sets of figures can be bought. Once we have
        enough data, we'll help you find the pack you have bought based on a
        few letters, and then fill in the rest of the form for you.</p>
        
        <fieldset>
            <legend>Pack</legend>

            <div class="field">
               <label for="manufacturer">Manufacturer</label>
               <input name="manufacturer" id="manufacturer"/>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field">
               <label for="pack">Pack name</label>
               <input name="pack" id="pack"/>
            </div>            

            [% FOREACH model = form_data.models %]

            <fieldset>
                <legend>Model</legend>
                
                <input type="hidden" name="models" value="[% model | html %]"/>
                
                <div class="field">
                   <label for="model_[% model | html %]">Model name</label>
                   <input name="model_[% model | html %]" id="model_[% model | html %]"/>
                </div>
                
                <div class="field">
                   <label for="quantity_[% model | html %]">Quantity in pack</label>
                   <input type="number" name="quantity_[% model | html %]" id="quantity_[% model | html %]" value="1"/>
                </div>
                
            </fieldset>
            
            [% END %]
            <div class="field">
                <input type="submit" name="action" value="Add another type of model" />
            </div>
            
        </fieldset>
        <input type="submit" name="action" value="Save and view" />
        <input type="submit" name="action" value="Save and add more" />
    </form>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
